<i> escaping Arizona,</i>

39:26.001 --> 39:31.583
<i> Wyatt Earp reemerges</i>
<i> in Hollywood, California,</i>

39:31.583 --> 39:34.834
<i> as a consultant in one of</i>
<i> America's newest industries--</i>

39:34.834 --> 39:38.417
<i> motion pictures.</i>

39:38.417 --> 39:39.792
Kirschner:
<i> Wyatt Earp had the advantage</i>

39:39.792 --> 39:41.834
<i> of living</i>
<i> to a ripe old age.</i>

39:41.834 --> 39:44.542
<i> He simply outlived</i>
<i> everybody else.</i>

39:44.542 --> 39:46.375
So, you know what they say,

39:46.375 --> 39:49.500
his history belongs
to the victors.

39:49.500 --> 39:51.500
Wyatt Earp:
We used to drive cattle
into Dodge City

39:51.500 --> 39:54.875
that would stretch
