40:02.041 --> 40:04.709
Narrator:
<i> By telling stories</i>
<i> about his past,</i>

40:04.709 --> 40:08.625
<i> Wyatt Earp immortalizes</i>
<i> the Old West in film.</i>

40:08.625 --> 40:10.625
Isenberg:
<i> Wyatt Earp decides</i>
<i> that if his life</i>

40:10.625 --> 40:12.792
<i> can be made into a film</i>
<i> the way he wants it made,</i>

40:12.792 --> 40:17.041
then the legacy will be the one
that he wants remembered.

40:17.041 --> 40:19.834
And in a lot of ways,
that's exactly what happens.

